  <Shw::Text::Body>To navigate the AdvancedTable with a keyboard</Shw::Text::Body>

  <ul class="shw-component-advanced-table-instruction-list">
    <li><strong>Arrow Keys</strong>: Move between the cells</li>
    <li><strong>Enter</strong>: Focuses the first interactive element in the cell. After press enter, you can tab to all
      focusable elements in the AdvancedTable.</li>
    <li><strong>Escape</strong>: If focused on an interactive element within a cell, it moves the focus back to the
      cell. After press escape, you can arrow key between the cells again.</li>
    <li><strong>Home</strong>: Move to first cell in the column</li>
    <li><strong>End</strong>: Move to last cell in the column</li>
    <li><strong>PageUp</strong>: Move to first cell in the row</li>
    <li><strong>PageDown</strong>: Move to last cell in the row</li>
  </ul>

